                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">&lt;Opinion from a level 20 Coercer&gt;
<br />

<br />
I choose Coercer for one big reason:
<br />

<br />
Recklessness.  This is a group haste buff.  Single Target Buffs are a PITA.  
<br />

<br />
Breeze is a terrific spell, but it is not convenient or fun to constantly watch the blue bars and Breeze those that need it.  Plus keeping it steady on myself and the healer(s).
<br />

<br />
It would drive me crazy to have to Breeze AND single target haste.
<br />

<br />
I wanted to be a good race.  I wanted to grow up in Qeynos.  But the lack of group haste forced my decision.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
