                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Since this thread has been resurrected, I will comment on how my coercer is doing.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />   He is level 30 now and I am enjoying it immensly.  However, I still don't know enough about illusionists to say if I would perfer one or not.  One of the things I do know is that illusionist adepts seem to drop all the time for me, but a coercer adept is a very rare drop indeed!  <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" />   But I am sure the illusionists are saying the same thing about coercer adepts.
