                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Qeynos players sell many Coercer spells
<br />
(not to mention other freeport classes - they are useless to Qeynos)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">there are * two * different types of Brokers in Freeport with entirely different merchandise inventories</span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
Freeport market (merchandise from Freeport players)
<br />
- any freeport broker has access
<br />

<br />
Qeynos market   (merchandise from Qeynos players)
<br />
- broker can <span style="font-weight: bold">only </span>be found on a small island in EastFreeport
<br />

<br />

<br />
the Qeynos broker has a 40% markup but there are still great deals even with that</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
